item.title: Dont Kow How To Portforward / Dont Work?
item.dc:creator: @leonscape leonscape
item.description:
@leonscape wrote:

change to no-ip then download utorrent then go to my computer right click press on properties and the go to advanced setting then to to environmental variables the look for a name called “ComSpec” open it and cange it to C:\Program Files (x86)\Java\jre6\bin then find “Path” change that to C:\Program Files (x86)\Java\jre6\bin
then there will be a bit at the top with to files called TEMP and TEP make a new one call it CLASSPATH and add C:\Program Files (x86)\Java\jre6\bin this to it the open uttorent go to options then preferences then change the port to 43594 or 5555 apply that then open no-ip tick your server address then open your source click run server and it should be online.

hope i helped
